      • setRunID

        public void setRunID(RunID runID)
        Sets Launch ID
        Specified by:
        setRunID in interface IStoreService
        Overrides:
        setRunID in class StoreServiceBase
        Parameters:
        runID - Steps: 1 - populate objects from DB ( Account, Orders, Execution, Position, etc ) 2 - setRunID("**OLD_LID"); This way, the system will update the old RunID without creating a new one. Please NOTE that if you are using IB, objects like account,orders, etc are being populate automatically. If you are backtesting, you have to do it yourself, if it matters.
